Jack Norton https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jack_Norton 0 Jack Norton (September 2, 1882 – October 15, 1958) was an American stage and film character actor who appeared in 184 films between 1934 and 1948, often playing drunks, although in real life he was a teetotaler.
